name: filepond

scripts.build: npm run scripts | npm run styles
scripts.styles: npm run styles:pretty && npm run styles:nano
scripts.styles:nano: cat src/css/* | npx node-sass | npx postcss --no-map --use autoprefixer --use cssnano | node banner-cli.js FilePond > dist/filepond.min.css
scripts.styles:pretty: cat src/css/* | npx node-sass | npx postcss --no-map --use autoprefixer | npx prettier --single-quote --parser css | node banner-cli.js FilePond > dist/filepond.css
